creator: thunderboltapps
descriptionHtml:
Pro Locker Protect privacy & security with password, pattern, fingerprint lock, app lock, gallery lock

☞ Pro locker can lock Gallery lock, SMS, Contacts, social media apps & messenger app, Settings, incoming calls and any app you choose. Prevent unauthorized access and guard privacy. Ensure security.

☞ Pro Locker or App Lock can hide pictures and videos with security. Hidden pictures and videos are vanished from Gallery and only visible in the photo and video vault. Protect private memories easily. No pin, no way.
☞ Pro locker has random keyboard and invisible pattern lock. No more worry people may peep the pin or pattern. More safe!

★ With Pro locker , you will:
Never worry about parents check your Snapchat, Musical.ly!
Never worry about friends borrow your phone to play games with mobile data again!
Never worry about a workmate gets your phone to look the gallery again!
Never worry about someone reads private data in your apps again!
Never worry about kids mess up Settings, send wrong messages, paying games again!

Pro locker can lock app, photos (gallery lock), videos and other private data with password lock, pattern lock or fingerprint.

Pro Locker is a free app locker that guards your privacy by preventing intruders & snoopers from peeping at your private data. It hides sensitive photos and videos by encrypting your Gallery, keeps children or snoopers away from messing up your settings, deleting important things, making in-app purchases or any such thing. You can customize app lock settings as you want, to make your phone more secure with just one app - App Lock

Pro locker can lock app, including:

- Social apps: App Lock can lock all apps No one can peep at your private chat any more.

- System apps: Can lock app including Contacts, SMS, Gallery, Videos, Email and so on. No one can mess up your settings for system apps.

- Payment apps: Can lock app used for making payments including Paypal, Google Pay, and many more. No one can use your wallet to purchase any item.

- Others: Pro Locker can lock any and every app, including social media, games and so on.

Pro Locker can lock photos and videos.

After locking gallery and video apps, no intruder can peep at your private photos and videos. No worry about privacy leakage.
